sample_rows.title: Mounting device and mounting method
sample_rows.abstract: PURPOSE: A mounting device and mounting method are provided to continuously mount a chip on a mounting part on which a coating agent is applied without waste. CONSTITUTION: A preform unit(22) applies a coating agent on a mounting part. A first adjusting unit(30) changes the perform line of the perform unit. A mounting unit(23) mounts a chip on a mounting part on which a coating agent is applied. A transferring unit(24) transfers a work from an upper side to a lower side. The transfer unit is made of a gripper feeder.

sample_rows.title: Inline belt furnace
sample_rows.abstract: PURPOSE: An inline belt furnace is provided to shorten the replacement time of an infrared lamp by easily controlling the infrared lamp through a heating unit guide unit. CONSTITUTION: A chamber includes a fist side and a second side which are parallel. A heating unit mounting groove(351) is formed on the first side and the second side. A heat unit guide groove(361) is formed on the second side and is spatially connected to the heat unit mounting groove. The heat unit guide groove is located lower than the heat unit mounting groove. A heat unit guide unit(340) is formed between the heat unit mounting groove of the first side and the heat unit guide groove of the second side and guides the movement of the heat unit.

sample_rows.abstract: The present invention relates to pyrazolopyridine of formula (I)     Derivatives and their pharmaceutical compositions and their use for the manufacture of a medicament for the treatment and / or prevention of diseases or conditions associated with nicotinamide adenine dinucleotide phosphate oxidase (NADPH oxidase).

sample_rows.title: Rechargeable battery
sample_rows.abstract: The secondary battery according to the present invention includes a core 7, an electrode tab 4 protruding from an end of the core, an electrode tab inducing device at the end of the core 7 and a cover plate 1. The electrode tab induction apparatus includes an insulating layer 6 in contact with the core end and a conductive layer 5 remote from the core end, and the electrode tab 4 is electrically connected to the conductive layer. It is electrically connected with the cover plate 1. In addition, the connecting member and the support plate (3) laminated between the conductive layer (5) and the cover plate (1) of the electrode tab induction apparatus further comprises a connecting member is the electrode tab (4) supporting the supporting plate (3) and electrode tab induction It is crimped | bonded between the conductive layers 5 of a device.
